It will take a while, but luckily you can do the things you like while waiting.
I'm sure all your guests will love it.ü•∞ Recipe for 10 sandwiches

Carrot "lox":
2 carrots
half a pound of sea salt (not for eating)
1 tablespoon soy sauce
1 tablespoon nutritional yeast
1 tablespoon oil
2 nori sheets
2 g dill 
Cashew nut cream:
30 g cashew nuts
1 tablespoon lemon juice
1 tablespoon nutritional yeast
1 teaspoon salt

Toppings:
capers
lemon pepper
dill

Bread:
10 sliced ‚Äã‚Äãwhole wheat toast

caption.text:
New Year's Eve is just a few days away. üòçüéâ‚ú®
This year, offer your guests this wonderful carrot "lox".
It will take a while, but luckily you can do the things you like while waiting.
I'm sure all your guests will love it.ü•∞ Recipe for 10 sandwiches

Carrot "lox":
2 carrots
half a pound of sea salt (not for eating)
1 tablespoon soy sauce
1 tablespoon nutritional yeast
1 tablespoon oil
2 nori sheets
2 g dill 
Cashew nut cream:
30 g cashew nuts
1 tablespoon lemon juice
1 tablespoon nutritional yeast
1 teaspoon salt

Toppings:
capers
lemon pepper
dill

Bread:
10 sliced ‚Äã‚Äãwhole wheat toast

Full resipe link in bio!

Have a nice weekend!
.

New Year's Eve is just a few days away. üòçüéâ‚ú®
This year, offer your guests this wonderful carrot "lox".
It will take a while, but luckily you can do the things you like while waiting.
I'm sure all your guests will love it.ü•∞ Recipe for 10 sandwiches

Carrot "lox":
2 carrots
half a pound of sea salt (not for eating)
1 tablespoon soy sauce
1 tablespoon nutritional yeast
1 tablespoon oil
2 nori sheets
2 g dill 
Cashew nut cream:
30 g cashew nuts
1 tablespoon lemon juice
1 tablespoon nutritional yeast
1 teaspoon salt

Toppings:
capers
lemon pepper
dill

Bread:
10 sliced ‚Äã‚Äãwhole wheat toast

Have a nice weekend!
